query:
INSERT INTO products (
  name, slug, description, shortDescription,
  regularPrice, salePrice,
  sku, stock,
  categoryId,
  tags,
  status,
  createdAt, updatedAt
) VALUES (
  'Destiny Analysis + Wutai Mountain Blessing Package',
  'destiny-analysis-blessing-79',
  'For just $79, you will not only receive our complete Destiny Energy Analysis Report, but also enjoy a personalized blessing ceremony performed by our team at China''s sacred Buddhist mountain—Wutai Mountain! Light up the path ahead for yourself and your loved ones.

**Your exclusive package includes:**

**Destiny Analysis Report (delivered within 3-5 days)**
- Personalized analysis based on your birth details, interpreting your destiny structure and energy interactions
- Examination of your major life cycles and yearly luck, helping you grasp key opportunities and precautions for 2025-2026
- Guidance covering career, wealth, relationships, health, and more
- Blending traditional Five Elements philosophy with modern life applications to provide practical advice

**Wutai Mountain Proxy Blessing Service (video delivered within 10-15 days)**
- You may choose Lighting a Lamp (illuminating your path and wisdom) or Offering Incense (praying for peace and dispelling obstacles)
- Our team will personally visit Wutai Mountain temples to record the entire blessing ceremony
- The video will include chanting of your name, your wishes, and the blessing process—ensuring transparency and authenticity
- Every lamp and incense stick is lit especially for you

**How to participate?**

1. Click the purchase link and select the $79 blessing package
2. After payment, please send your name, birth information, and blessing preference (lamp or incense) to: seondo@cneraart.com
3. You will receive your Destiny Energy Analysis Report via email within 3-5 business days
4. The blessing video will be sent to your email within 10-15 days after the ceremony is completed

**Why choose this upgrade?**
- More than prediction—infuse your life with blessed energy
- Ancient wisdom + sacred ceremony, dual protection
- Full transparency with video proof—sincere and trustworthy
- Suitable for various wishes: career success, family harmony, turning luck around, academic achievement, and more

One report, one lamp, one wish, one transformation. May we join hands, knock on the door of destiny, and welcome a bright future.

**Note:** The blessing service is a proxy religious offering. We respect all beliefs—sincerity is what matters. Our service strictly adheres to traditional cultural interpretations and is intended to provide directional guidance only. All results are for reference purposes.',
  'Complete destiny analysis report plus personalized Wutai Mountain blessing ceremony with video proof',
  79.00, NULL,
  'FORTUNE-BLESSING-002', 999,
  1,
  '["destiny", "fortune", "bazi", "wutai-mountain", "blessing", "lamp-offering", "incense-offering"]',
  'published',
  NOW(), NOW()
);
